      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Andrew Sanderson joined the Foreign and Commonwealth Office as Finance Director in August 2016.</p>

<p>His previous job was as Director of Financial Planning at the Department of Health. Before that he worked in a variety of finance and policy roles in the Department of Health, HM Treasury and the Department for Work and Pensions.</p>

<p>He is a CIPFA-qualified accountant.</p>
</div>
      </section>

